<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Scott Derrickson is a writer and director, known for <a href="/title/tt1922777?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Sinister</a> (2012), <a href="/title/tt0404032?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">The Exorcism of Emily Rose</a> (2005) and <a href="/title/tt2377322?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Deliver Us from Evil</a> (2014).            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0220600/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        

                        
                        
